ace roughness are achieved; but this also produces a larger Te defect\ndensity, adding n-type carriers. This work provides key information necessary\nfor optimizing thin film quality in this fundamentally and technologically\nimportant class of materials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Sep 2017 17:07:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-04"}
