es of equilibrium of Venus-like planets as functions of the\nphysical parameters of the system. These results are detailed in\nAuclair-Desrotour et al. (2017a) and Auclair-Desrotour et al. (2017b).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Sep 2017 12:52:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-28"}
