ens during the construction of the property tree. Thus we experimentally\ndemonstrate the usefulness of attentive neural architectures for the proposed\njoint model, showcasing a further improvement of two percentage points in edge\nF1 score for our application.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Sep 2017 15:50:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 19 Mar 2018 13:51:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-20"}
